  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>UNLEASH YOUR INNER SPEEDRUNNER</strong></i></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><strong>Highlights</strong><li>Tons of handcrafted levels + unique post-story hard levels<br></li><li>Banging synthwave soundtrack<br></li><li>Hours of fun and replayability as you master and break levels<br></li><li>Become a speedrunner and beat records collecting trophies</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488650/extras/ea5d332986665843a4eb1b97b5f41416.poster.avif?t=1726250751\" width=616 height=110 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488650/extras/ea5d332986665843a4eb1b97b5f41416.webm?t=1726250751\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488650/extras/ea5d332986665843a4eb1b97b5f41416.mp4?t=1726250751\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>\"This is a smoooth noodle\" - A cool customer</i><br><br>Velocity Noodle has ultra-smooth movement, don't spill your noodles when you combine movement skills and break levels to go fast!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488650/extras/54ac43744f04df5925b7366cdcc5f19d.poster.avif?t=1726250751\" width=616 height=110 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488650/extras/54ac43744f04df5925b7366cdcc5f19d.webm?t=1726250751\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488650/extras/54ac43744f04df5925b7366cdcc5f19d.mp4?t=1726250751\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>\"This town sucks. - Random Noodle City resident\"</i><br><br>All the traps and alternative routes are handcrafted to maximize enjoyment! Have fun jumping and teleporting past traps or getting chased by the A.D.S. (Anti-Delivery Service a.k.a. the food police).<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488650/extras/ec03a5ce924a60eab6f85bcab842a6d6.poster.avif?t=1726250751\" width=616 height=110 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488650/extras/ec03a5ce924a60eab6f85bcab842a6d6.webm?t=1726250751\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488650/extras/ec03a5ce924a60eab6f85bcab842a6d6.mp4?t=1726250751\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>\"Ooo so shiny!\" - Proud mom</i><br><br>The faster you go, the more you help out your little noodle stand. Break records and get shiny trophies and who knows, it might unlock even more stuff.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488650/extras/db44e11ce68c46969c3e2f797afccba3.poster.avif?t=1726250751\" width=616 height=110 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488650/extras/db44e11ce68c46969c3e2f797afccba3.webm?t=1726250751\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488650/extras/db44e11ce68c46969c3e2f797afccba3.mp4?t=1726250751\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>\"Woof\" - Dog</i><br><br>You can pet dog. That's all.<br><br>Buy your noodles today and enjoy!",
